.html Una mujer de 44 a\u00f1os, asesinada por su pareja de 30 pu\u00f1aladas en La Vi\u00f1uela] in diariosur.es {{in lang|es}}</ref> \n* March 24: A man allegedly runs over his partner three times until he kills her in [[Toledo, Spain|Toledo]].<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/clm/provincias/toledo/Detenido-Madrid-atropellarla-A-5-Toledo_0_756274775.html La Guardia Civil detiene al hombre acusado de asesinar a su pareja al atropellarla en Toledo] en [[eldiario.es]] {{in lang|es}}</ref> \n* March 30: A woman (48) is allegedly suffocated by her old partner (38) in [[Albox]] ([[Province of Almer\u00eda|Almer\u00eda]])<ref>[https://www.elespanol.com/reportajes/20180401/carmen-pidio-ayuda-maltratador-denegaron-final-mato/296220935_0.html Carmen pidi\u00f3 ayuda contra su maltratador, pero se la denegaron y al final la mat\u00f3] in elespanol.con {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* April 9: A man (41) stabs and kills his wife (40) in front of their children in [[Blanes]], [[Province of Girona|Girona]].<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20180409/un-hombre-mata-a-su-mujer-en-blanes-6743949 Un hombre mata a su mujer delante de los dos hijos de la pareja en Blanes] in elperiodico.com {{in lang|es}}</ref> \n* April 11: A man (46) allegedly kills his wife (39) in [[Murcia]]. She was as Colombian human rights defendant who had to leave her country due to [[Revolutionary Armed Forces of Colombia|FARC]] threats.<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/lapalmaahora/sociedad/Asesinan-Murcia-La_Palma-Amnistia-Internacional_0_760124989.html Asesinan en Murcia a una defensora de los derechos humanos que residi\u00f3 en La Palma acogida por Amnist\u00eda Internacional ] in eldiario.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* April 20: In [[Vitoria-Gasteiz]] a man kills his ex-wife (43) and her mother, barricades himself in his house while the police surround the building, throws himself out of the window and falls on an inflatable mattress prepared by firefighters that saves his life.<ref>[http://m.noticiasdealava.eu