itcase in a burnt industrial warehouse in Madrid. After identifying the corpse, police proceed to search for his partner (45) (self nicknamed \"the king of [[cachopo]]\"), who is finally found on November 16 working under a false identity in a pub in [[Zaragoza]].<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/sociedad/Gobierno-confirma-cachopo-violencia-machista_0_841316190.html El Gobierno confirma el asesinato de la novia de 'el rey del cachopo' como violencia machista] en eldiario.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* August 14: A man (39) stabs his partner (21) in [[D\u00farcal]], [[Province of Granada|Granada]].<ref>[https://www.ideal.es/granada/provincia-granada/cuarta-victima-asesinada-20180814113847-nt.html La cuarta v\u00edctima asesinada a manos de su pareja en Granada en lo que va de a\u00f1o] in ideal.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* August 19: A man (56) shoots his wife (50) in front of their two sons in [[Cabana de Berganti\u00f1os]], [[Province of A Coru\u00f1a|A Coru\u00f1a]].<ref>[https://www.lavozdegalicia.es/noticia/carballo/cabana-de-bergantinos/2018/08/19/detenido-hombre-matar-esposa-cabana-bergantinos/00031534699057024699506.htm Detenido un hombre por matar a su esposa en Cabana de Berganti\u00f1os] in lavozdegalicia.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* August 23: A man (27) stabs his girlfriend (35). A few days before they had announced their marriage compromise. In [[Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20180823/451415016808/asesina-mujer-nou-barris-acuchillada.html Detenido tras asesinar a su novia a pu\u00f1aladas en Nou Barris] in lavanguardia.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* August 27: A man (57) strangles his partner (60) in [[Orihuela]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/cv/Nuevo-asesinato-machista-Detenido-Orihuela_0_808069250.html Nuevo asesinato machista: detenido un hombre en Orihuela por matar a su pareja] in eldiario.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* August 27: A man (48) beats to death his wife (38). His mother helped him clean the crime