003379.html Un ni\u00f1o de seis a\u00f1os huy\u00f3 de su padre y alert\u00f3 del asesinato de su madre y su hermano en Tenerife] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 1: The stabbed corpse of a woman (47) is found in [[Parla]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]]. She went back to live with his boyfriend (42), despite him having been already denounced 3 times by her for mistreatment.<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/madrid/2019/05/05/5cceb77dfdddff278f8b45d0.html Un hombre mata a su pareja de 47 a\u00f1os de nueve pu\u00f1aladas en Parla] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 9: A woman (42) appears in her bed dead, naked and with a flower in her bust. Her partner (39) is arrested at the airport. In [[Torre Pacheco]], [[Province of Murcia|Murcia]].<ref>[https://torrepacheco.laverdad.es/actualidad/detienen-presunto-autor-20190510095441-nt.html Detenido en el aeropuerto de Alicante el presunto autor del crimen machista en Torre Pacheco cuando iba a huir] in laverdad.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 30: A man (47) shoots his partner (39) in the head in [[Ag\u00fcimes]], [[Province of Las Palmas|Las Palmas de Gran Canaria]].<ref>[https://www.eldia.es/sucesos/2019/05/31/ingeniero-gran-canaria-mata-pareja/980148.html Un ingeniero de Gran Canaria mata a su pareja y se suicida con su escopeta] in eldia.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* June 3: A man (53) shots his wife (51) with a shotgun, then commits suicide in [[Izn\u00e1jar]], [[Province of C\u00f3rdoba (Spain)|C\u00f3rdoba]].<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/andalucia/2019/06/03/5cf5102a21efa05d258b4698.html Encuentran a una pareja muerta en su casa por disparos de escopeta] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* June 10: A man (48) stabs his partner (29)because she wanted to break up with him. In [[Alboraya]], [[Province of Valencia|Valencia]]. She is the 1000th murdered women since there are official data in 2003.<ref>[https://www.lasprovincias.es/sucesos/perfil-pareja-asesinato-machista-port-saplaya-20190610151632-nt.html Perfil de la pareja: una camarera y el cocinero de una pizzer\u00eda de Port Saplaya] in lasprovicias.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* June 14: A woman (49) dies stabbed by his partner (46), who was on probation after having murdered his previous wife in 2002 with an iron cord. After killing her, he set the building on fire, also dying. In [[C\u00f3rdoba, Spain|C\u00f3rdoba]].<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20190614/mujer-hombre-muerto-incendio-cordoba-7504988 Un asesino machista, en libertad condicional, sospechoso de matar a otra mujer en C\u00f3rdoba] in elperiodico.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* July 2: A man (42) kills his wife (42) with a hammer in [[Rute]], [[Province of C\u00f3rdoba (Spain)|C\u00f3rdoba]] y luego se entrega a la polic\u00eda.<ref>[https://elpais.com/sociedad/2019/07/02/actualidad/1562062193_507915.html Un hombre mata a su pareja en C\u00f3rdoba y huye con sus dos hijos a Madrid] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*July 3: Police found evidence that a woman (25) found dead on 9 September 2018 in [[Granollers]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]] had been murdered by her husband.<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20190703/detencion-granollers-mujer-hallada-muerta-rio-7535234  Detenida la pareja de la mujer hallada muerta hace un a\u00f1o en Granollers] in elperiodico.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*July 13: A woman (47) is stabbed by her husband in [[Elche]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20190713/463437346211/mujer-elche-asesinada-crimen-machista.html Una mujer de 47 a\u00f1os asesinada en Elche en un nuevo crimen machista] in lavanguardia.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*July 15: In [[Almer\u00eda]] it is found the heavely descomposed corpse of a woman (39). Autopsy determned she had been stabbed. Police detaines her partner(50).<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20191031/detenido-muerte-mujer-almeria-7708652 Detenido por la muerte de expareja, cuyo cad\u00e1ver apareci\u00f3 en julio en A