nce of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.telecinco.es/informativos/sociedad/yulia-asesinada-violencia-machista_18_2860995016.html Yulia, degollada por su marido, no hab\u00eda denunciado] in telecinco.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n\n===Other cases===\n*January 1: 4 men (19, 21, 22 and 24 years old) [[Gang rape|rape]] a woman (19) in [[Callosa d'en Sarri\u00e0]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.elconfidencial.com/espana/comunidad-valenciana/2019-01-08/callosa-pamplona-manada-violacion_1745614/ La jueza instruye el caso de La Manada de Callosa como violaci\u00f3n y con penas m\u00e1ximas] in elconfidencial.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 8: A sentence of [[Supreme Court of Spain]] concludes that a man hitting his (female) partner is always gender violence, even if both have mutually hit each other.<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2019/01/08/5c34c8d9fc6c83eb128b467b.html El Supremo: \"Toda agresi\u00f3n de un hombre a una mujer en relaci\u00f3n de pareja o ex pareja es violencia de g\u00e9nero\"] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* February 3: Six men are detained for allegedly gang raping an 18-year-old woman in [[Sabadell]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.cope.es/actualidad/espana/noticias/manada-sabadell-los-mossos-interrogaran-hoy-los-detenidos-20190204_345578 La 'manada' de Sabadell: Los mossos interrogar\u00e1n hoy a los 6 detenidos] in cope.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*November 30: A man was arrested for the alleged murder of his wife (38) in [[Vic\u00e1lvaro]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]], but was acquitted in March 2020 when the autopsy confirmed that the cause of death was a heart attack.<ref>[https://www.elespanol.com/sociedad/20200304/alexia-infarto-justicia-absuelve-detenido-presunto-homicidio/472203254_0.html Alexia muri\u00f3 de un infarto: absuelto el detenido por un presunto homicidio machista ] in elespanol.com {{in lang|es}</ref>\n\n== 2020 ==\n===Gender violence murders===\n*January 6: A man (27) is arrested accused of killing his partner (28) and their 3 year old daughter in [[Esplugues de Llobregat]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[http://www.rtve.es/noticias/20200106/detenido-hombre-matar-su-mujer-su-hija-su-casa-esplugues-llobregat-barcelona/1994951.shtml Detenido un hombre por matar a su mujer y a su hija en su casa de Esplugues de Llobregat, Barcelona] in rtve.es</ref>\n*January 12: A man (53) shots his partner (61) then commits suicide. In [[Puertollano]], [[Province of Ciudad Real|Ciudad Real]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20200113/472860131699/muertos-hombre-mujer-violencia-puertollano-ciudad-real.html Un hombre mata a su pareja y se suicida en Puertollano] in lavanguardia.com</ref>\n*January, 18: A [[Mossos d'Esquadra|''Mosso d'Esquadra'']] (42) shots his partner (29) in [[Terrassa]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20200119/472964333206/mosso-terrassa-violencia-machista.html Un Mosso mata a tiros a su expareja y se suicida in Terrassa] in lavanguardia.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 22: A man (50) kills his wife (43) in front of their 11 and 14 years old sons. In [[La Puebla de Almoradiel]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]].<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2020/01/22/5e27fb1421efa008218b468d.html Mata a su esposa en La Puebla de Almoradiel en presencia de sus dos hijos] in elmundo.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 22: A man (77) stabs his wife (73) in [[Caniles]], [[Province of Granada|Granada]].<ref>[https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4126864/0/detenido-por-matar-a-punaladas-a-su-mujer-en-caniles-granada/ Un hombre de 77 a\u00f1os mata a pu\u00f1aladas a su mujer, de 73, en Caniles (Granada)] in 20minutos.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 25: A man (81) stabs his wife (79), then commits suicide. In [[A Pastoriza]], [[Province of Lugo|Lugo]]. The family indicates that the agressor had senile [[dementia]].<ref>[https://www.lavozdegalicia.es/noticia/lugo/a-pastoriza/2020/01/26/mujer-asesinada-pastoriza-murio-punalada-costado/00031580068839323575648.htm La mujer asesinada en A Pastoriza muri\u00f3 de una pu\u00f1alada en un costado] in lavozdegalicia.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 28: A man (45) suffocates his partner (40) in [[Sant Joan Desp\u00ed]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]] and is arrested at the airport while he was trying to escape.<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200127/un-hombre-asesina-a-su-pareja-en-sant-joan-despi-7824877 https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200127/un-hombre-asesina-a-su-pareja-en-sant-joan-despi-7824877] in elperiodico.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 3: An ex-[[Spanish Legion|legionary]] alleguedly kills in [[Gij\u00f3n]], [[Asturias]], his expartner, then scapes.<ref>[https://www.elcomercio.es/asturias/encuentran-muerta-mujer-calzada-gijon-presunto-caso-violencia-genero-20200203151255-nt.html Encuentran muerta a una mujer en Gij\u00f3n en un caso de violencia de g\u00e9nero] in elcomercio.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 7: A man (47) beheads his partner (49) in [[Lugo]].<ref>[https://www.republica.com/2020/02/09/el-novio-de-la-mujer-asesinada-en-lugo-pasara-a-disposicion-judicial/# El novio de la mujer asesinada en Lugo pasar\u00e1 a disposici\u00f3n judicial] in republica.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 8: A legionary (24) stabs his expartner (38) in [[Granada]].<ref>[https://www.ideal.es/granada/mujer-fallecida-apunalada-por-su-expareja-tras-20200208192928-nt.html Un legionario destinado en Viator mata a pu\u00f1aladas a su expareja en Granada] in ideal.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 17: A man (59) stabs his partner (34) in [[Moraira]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.diarioinformacion.com/sucesos/2020/02/19/pareja-mujer-asesinada-moraira-confiesa/2236393.html El marido de la mujer asesinada en Moraira se entrega y confiesa el crimen] in diarioinformacion.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 26: A man (51) shoots his wife (43) in front of their 4 years old son, then commits suicide. In [[Aznalc\u00f3llar]], [[Province of Sevilla|Sevilla]].<ref>[https://www.edmradio.es/2020/02/26/una-mujer-es-asesinada-por-su-pareja-en-aznalcollar/ UNA MUJER ES ASESINADA POR SU PAREJA EN AZNALC\u00d3LLAR] in edmradio.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 26: A man (76) stabs his wife (75) in [[Fuenlabrada]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]].<ref>[https://alcabodelacalle.es/un-hombre-asesina-a-su-mujer-en-su-casa-de-fuenlabrada-y-despues-intenta-suicidarse Un hombre asesina a su mujer en su casa de Fuenlabrada y despu\u00e9s intenta suicidarse] in alcabodelacalle.es] (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 2: A man (69) stabs his ex-wife (65) in [[Posadas, Spain|Posadas]], [[Province of C\u00f3rdoba|C\u00f3rdoba]] then tries to commit suicide.<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/andalucia/2020/03/02/5e5d0627fc6c835f3a8b461f.html Un hombre de 69 a\u00f1os asesina a su mujer en Posadas (C\u00f3rdoba)] in elmundo.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 9: A man shots his girldfriend (37) in [[Villanueva de Castell\u00f3n]], [[Province of Valencia|Valencia]].<ref>[https://www.lasprovincias.es/sucesos/joven-muere-recibir-20200309001635-ntvo.html?ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.es%2F Un hombre con antecedentes policiales mata a su pareja de un tiro en la cabeza en Villanueva de Castell\u00f3n] in lasprovincias.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 11: A man (60) stabs his wife (56) and their daughter (24) in [[Abanto y Ci\u00e9rvana-Abanto Zierbena|Abanto Zierbena]], [[Biscay]].<ref>[https://www.levante-emv.com/espana/2020/03/11/madre-hija-halladas-muertas-vizcaya/1988275.html Detenido tras matar a su mujer y su hija en Vizcaya] in levante-emv.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 19: A man (35) kills his wife (35) in front of their children in [[Almassora]], [[Province of Castell\u00f3n|Castell\u00f3n]].<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200320/un-hombre-mata-a-su-mujer-delante-de-sus-hijos-en-castellon-7897934 Un hombre mata a su mujer delante de sus hijos en Castell\u00f3n] in elperiodico.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*April 4: A man (62) strangles his wife (78) in [[Las Palmas de Gran Canaria]].<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/canariasahora/sociedad/delegacion-asesinato-machista-Palmas-Gran-Canaria_0_1013148842.html Asesinada por su marido una mujer de 78 a\u00f1os en Las Palmas de Gran Canaria] in eldiario.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Human_rights_in_Spain#Migrant agricultural workers in Southern Spain|Violence against migrant agricultural workers in Spain]]\n* [[List of incidents of violence against women]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.violenciagenero.igualdad.mpr.gob.es/otrasFormas/home.htm Violence against women] in Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}\n* [http://ibasque.com/mujeres-muertas-en-espana-por-violencia-machista/ MUJERES ASESINADAS EN ESPA\u00d1A POR VIOLENCIA DE G\u00c9NERO y MACHISTA en 2019] in ibasque.com {{in lang|es}}\n\n[[Category:Incidents of violence against women|*]]\n[[Category:Violence against women in Spain|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of events in Spain|Incidents of violence against women]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\nThis is a '''list of incidents of violence against women in Spain'''. The [[Ministry of Health (Spain)|Ministry of Health, Social Services and Equality]] publishes statistics on [[violence against women]] and counts every death. Also, [[media in Spain]] reports every case of violence against women that results in a death.\n\nIn the last decade about 700 women have been killed in Spain by their partners or ex-partners.<ref>{{cite web|title=700 mujeres muertas por violencia de g\u00e9nero en la \u00faltima d\u00e9cada|url=http://www.elmundo.es/espana/2013/11/03/52766e7363fd3d62298b456e.html|publisher=El Mundo|date=2013-11-03|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref> Since 1999, the number of killed women is over 1,000.\n\n{{Expand list|date=April 2018}}\n\n== Before 2003 ==\n* November 13, 1992: [[Alcasser Girls]]: 3 teenage girls from Alc\u00e0sser, Valencia, Spain, were kidnapped, raped, assaulted and murdered after hitchhiking to get to a nightclub.\n* April 1993: [[Kidnapping of Anabel Segura]]: 2 men kidnap and later (when she was trying to escape) murder a 22-year-old woman.<ref>[https://elpais.com/diario/1993/04/16/madrid/734959454_850215.html El padre de Ia secuestrada en La Moraleja dirige una empresa de ingenier\u00eda] in [[El Pa\u00eds]]</ref>\n* December 17, 1997: [[Ana Orantes]]:  After her testimony was shown on a television program, she was killed by her last husband.<ref>{{Cite news |last=S\u00e1nchez Hidalgo |first=Emilio |title=Recordando a Ana Orantes, cuyo testimonio cambi\u00f3 la visi\u00f3n de la violencia machista |url=https://verne.elpais.com/verne/2017/09/30/articulo/1506779392_536978.html |date=September 30, 2017 |access-date=November 27, 2017 |newspaper=[[El Pa\u00eds]] |agency=Verne |language=es}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=El Khattat |first=Mohamed |title=Un hombre mata a su ex mujer prendi\u00e9ndole fuego tras atarla |url=http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/1997/diciembre/18/nacional/malostratos.html |date=November 18, 1997 |access-date=September 30, 2017 |newspaper=[[ABC (Spain)|ABC]] |location=Granada |language=es}}</ref> It caused a big repercussion about gender violence, and as a consequence, the restructuring of the [[Criminal Code of Spain]].<ref>{{Cite news |last=E. Ram\u00edrez |first=Carlota |title=El asesinato de Ana Orantes: un antes y un despu\u00e9s en la violencia machista en Espa\u00f1a |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.es/2017/11/17/el-asesinato-de-ana-orantes-un-antes-y-un-despues-en-la-violencia-machista-en-espana_a_23280596/ |date=November 17, 2017 |access-date=November 27, 2017 |newspaper=[[Huffington Post]] |language=es}}</ref>\n* April 20, 1997: [[Murder of Eva Blanco]]:  Spanish high school student was murdered in Algete, Community of Madrid. The case remained unsolved until 2015\n* October 9/10, 1999: [[Murder of Roc\u00edo Wanninkhof]]: a Dutch-Spanish teenage girl who was murdered in her hometown of Mijas\n\n== 2003 - 2011 ==\n*Women killed in [[gender violence]] cases\n**2003: 71 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/DatosViolenciaGeneroAno2003.pdf Official data] of [[Ministry of Health (Spain)|Ministry of Health]] website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2004: 72 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2004.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2005: 57 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2005.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2006: 69 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2006.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2007: 71 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2007.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2008: 76 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2008.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2009: 56 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2009.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2010: 73 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/Datos_violencia_genero_ano_2010.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2011: 62 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/mortales/docs/2011.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* 17 May 2003: [[Murder of Sandra Palo]]: A woman (22) is raped, run over by a car and burnt alive by 4 minors (in the 14-18 age range) in Madrid.<ref>[http://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20180518/443637789090/sandra-palo-asesino-rafita-rafael-fernandez-garcia-menor-crimen-quince-anos-las-caras-del-mal.html \u2018El Rafita\u2019, el menor que viol\u00f3, quem\u00f3 y asesin\u00f3 a Sandra Palo] in lavanguardia.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* 24 May 2003: A man (34) shoots his wife (29) in [[La Puebla de H\u00edjar]] [[Province of Teruel|Teruel]].<ref>[https://elpais.com/diario/2003/05/24/sociedad/1053727203_850215.html Un hombre mata de 11 tiros a su mujer, candidata del PP a un pueblo de Teruel] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref> He killed another woman in 2019.\n* 24 January 2009: [[Murder of Marta del Castillo]]:  a Spanish high school student who disappeared and was presumably murdered \n* 14 August 2009: Murder of Sonia Carabantes: Murder of a 17-year-old girl that helped to solve the case of [[Murder of Roc\u00edo Wanninkhof|Roc\u00edo Wanninkhof]]\n\n== 2012- 2014 ==\n*Women killed in gender violence cases:\n**2012: 52 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/pdf/V_Mortales_2012.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2013: 54 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/pdf/Espana_2013.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n**2014: 55 women<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.msssi.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/pdf/2014.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* June 30, 2012: A man kills and butchers his partner in [[Cadrete]].<ref>[https://www.heraldo.es/noticias/aragon/zaragoza_provincia/zaragoza/2014/08/20/la_familia_descuartizada_cadrete_acusa_tambien_asesinato_dos_cunados_305655_301.html La familia de la descuartizada de Cadrete acusa tambi\u00e9n de asesinato a dos cu\u00f1ados] in [[Heraldo de Arag\u00f3n]].</ref>\n\n== 2015 ==\n\n60 women were killed in Spain in cases of gender violence<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.igualdad.mpr.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/pdf/31_12_2015-act.pdf Official data] of [[Ministry of Health (Spain)|Ministry of Health]] website:</ref>\n\n* January 12: A man (70) kills his ex-partner (70) and her sister (64) in [[Elche]]. Later, he commits suicide. Five minutes of silence were observed for the double crime.<ref>{{cite web|title=El acusado de matar a su exmujer y su excu\u00f1ada us\u00f3 una barra de hierro y dej\u00f3 una nota autoinculpatoria|url=http://www.lasprovincias.es/sucesos/201501/13/acusado-matar-exmujer-excunada-20150113120021.html|publisher=Las Provincias|date=2015-01-13|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Un hombre mata a su ex pareja y a la hermana de \u00e9sta y luego se ahorca en Elche|url=http://www.publico.es/sociedad/sucesos/hombre-mata-ex-pareja-y.html|publisher=P\u00fablico|date=2015-01-12|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Un hombre mata a su ex pareja y a la hermana en Elche y se suicida|url=http://www.elmundo.es/comunidad-valenciana/2015/01/12/54b3efda22601d4c488b4581.html|publisher=El Mundo|date=2015-01-12|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=La mujer asesinada en Elx, primera v\u00edctima mortal de violencia machista de 2015|url=http://www.levante-emv.com/sucesos/2015/01/12/mujer-asesinada-elx-primera-victima/1211291.html|publisher=Levante-EMV|date=2015-01-12|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* January 17: A woman (69) is killed in [[Orba, Alicante]]. Her partner flees to Germany, where he confesses the crime at the airport to police. Silent demonstrations were held in Alicante and Valencia.<ref>{{cite web|title=El presunto homicida de Alicante asfixi\u00f3 a la mujer 3 d\u00edas antes de confesar|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20150120/54423560903/el-presunto-homicida-de-alicante-asfixio-a-la-mujer-3-dias-antes-de-confesar.html|publisher=La Vanguardia|date=2015-01-20|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* January 21: A man (44) kills his wife (39) and then he commits suicide in [[Terrassa]]. They had a 6-year-old child. About 200 people meet in front of the city hall to protest against violence against women.<ref>{{cite web|title=Mata a pu\u00f1aladas a su mujer y luego se suicida en su piso de Terrassa|url=http://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20150121/54423831212/investigan-homicidio-de-una-mujer-y-suicidio-de-un-hombre-en-casa-de-terrassa.html|publisher=La Vanguardia|date=2015-01-21|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* February 4: A woman is stabbed to death by a man in [[Arrecife]]. They met some months previously.<ref>{{cite web|title=Mata a una mujer en Lanzarote y lo detienen cuando hu\u00eda de la isla|url=http://www.eldiario.es/politica/Mata-mujer-Lanzarote-detienen-isla_0_353115748.html|publisher=El Diario|date=2015-02-04|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* February 6: A woman is strangled in [[Ronda]]. About 30 people protest against the crime.<ref>{{cite web|title=La autopsia revela que la turista alojada en Ronda muri\u00f3 estrangulada...|url=http://www.malagahoy.es/article/malaga/1956284/la/autopsia/revela/la/turista/alojada/ronda/murio/estrangulada.html|publisher=M\u00e1laga Hoy|date=2015-02-06|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* February 12: A man (47) stabs to death his partner (38) in [[Valencia]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Detenido un hombre por matar a su pareja sentimental a cuchilladas|url=http://www.elmundo.es/comunidad-valenciana/2015/02/12/54dc7a6be2704ea6488b457e.html|publisher=El Mundo|date=2015-02-12|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* March 9: A man (75) confesses to have killed his wife (76) six months before in [[San Miguel de Salinas]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Hallan el cad\u00e1ver de una mujer tras confesar su pareja que la mat\u00f3 a bastonazos|url=http://www.diarioinformacion.com/sucesos/2015/03/11/hallan-algorfa-cadaver-mujer-confesar/1608456.html|publisher=Diario Informaci\u00f3n|date=2015-03-11|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* March 10: A woman (43) is killed by her partner in [[X\u00e0bia]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Una mujer fallece tras ser golpeada con una sart\u00e9n por su marido ante sus hijos en X\u00e0bia|url=http://www.levante-emv.com/sucesos/2015/03/10/mujer-fallece-golpeada-sarten-marido/1236418.html|publisher=Levante-EMV|date=2015-03-10|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* March 12: A woman (23) is thrown out of a van driven by her husband (24) in [[C\u00e1ceres, Spain|C\u00e1ceres]] and dies due to the injuries.<ref>{{cite web|title=Fallece una joven cerca de C\u00e1ceres tras ser arrojada desde un veh\u00edculo|url=http://www.elperiodicoextremadura.com/noticias/caceres/fallece-joven-cerca-caceres-ser-arrojada-vehiculo_859568.html|publisher=El Peri\u00f3dico de Extremadura|date=2015-03-12|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sanidad confirma que la muerte de Tamara Sim\u00f3n fue un crimen de violencia de g\u00e9nero|url=http://www.hoy.es/caceres/201503/17/sanidad-confirma-muerte-joven-20150317123410.html|publisher=Hoy|date=2015-03-17|accessdate=2015-10-06|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* March 29: A man kills his wife (31) in [[Alhaur\u00edn de la Torre]] and then he commits suicide. About 100 people gather in the city hall square to protest against the crime.<ref>{{cite web|title=Hallan muerta a una pareja en un posible caso de violencia machista|url=http://www.diariosur.es/interior/201503/30/hallan-muerta-pareja-posible-20150330010847.html|publisher=Diario Sur|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-10-09|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=La autopsia confirma que la muerte en Alhaur\u00edn es otro caso de violencia de g\u00e9nero|url=http://www.laopiniondemalaga.es/municipios/2015/03/30/hallan-cadaveres-pareja-casa-alhaurin/754838.html|publisher=La Opini\u00f3n de M\u00e1laga|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-10-09|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* March 30: A man shoots his wife (24) in [[Lleida]] and then attempts suicide.<ref>{{cite web|title=Un hombre mata a su mujer de un tiro en Lleida e intenta suicidarse|url=http://ccaa.elpais.com/ccaa/2015/03/30/catalunya/1427732666_717772.html|publisher=El Pa\u00eds|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-10-09|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* April 2: A man (34) stabs his wife (29) to death in [[Vitoria-Gasteiz]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Una mujer muere acuchillada presuntamente por su pareja en Vitoria. Diario de Noticias de Alava|url=http://www.noticiasdealava.com/2015/04/02/araba/detenido-en-vitoria-por-acuchillar-hasta-la-muerte-a-su-pareja-en-el-domicilio-conyugal|publisher=Noticias de \u00c1lava|date=2015-04-02|accessdate=2015-10-09|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n* May 3: A man (50) kills his wife (47) and her boss (57) in [[Sorbas]] and [[N\u00edjar]] respectively.<ref>{{cite web|title=Un hombre se entrega a la Guardia Civil tras matar a su mujer y al jefe de \u00e9sta en Almer\u00eda|url=http://www.elmundo.es/andalucia/2015/05/03/55460fe6268e3eba1d8b4576.html|publisher=El Mundo|date=2015-05-03|accessdate=2015-10-09|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n== 2016 ==\n===Gender violence murders===\n49 women were killed in [[gender violence]] cases.<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.igualdad.mpr.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/pdf/VM_Ficha_2016_2.pdf Official data] of Ministry of Health website</ref>\n*January 4: A man (41) strangles his partner (43) in [[Madrid]].<ref>[https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/2642473/0/mujer-asesinada/violencia-machista/estrangulada-pareja/ Muere una mujer de 43 a\u00f1os estrangulada por su pareja en Madrid] in 20minutos.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 5: A man stabs his partner (33) in [[Gal\u00e1pagos, Guadalajara|Gal\u00e1pagos]], [[Province of Guadalajara|Guadalajara]].<ref>[https://politica.elpais.com/politica/2016/01/05/actualidad/1451981676_471998.html Una mujer es asesinada por su pareja a pu\u00f1aladas en Guadalajara] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref> \n*January 7: A man (27) drowns his partner (21) in a  [[swamp]] in [[Alange]], [[Province of Badajoz|Badajoz]].<ref>[http://www.hoy.es/prov-badajoz/martes-comienza-juicio-20180122195510-nt.html El juicio por el asesinato de una joven en Alange comienza este martes] in hoy.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* January 11: A man is detained in [[Quintanar de la Orden]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]] after his wife (59) is found stabbed. He is released 4 days later because it is found that the DNA of the knife was his brother's (the brother-in-law's victim),<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/sociedad/2016/11/14/5829b069268e3e2d588b4594.html Detenido el hermano del \"inocente\" encarcelado por matar a su mujer en enero] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref> who confessed the crime.<ref>[http://www.abc.es/espana/castilla-la-mancha/toledo/pueblos/abci-asesino-confeso-intento-suicidarse-despues-matar-cunada-201611152109_noticia.html El asesino confeso intent\u00f3 suicidarse despu\u00e9s de matar a su cu\u00f1ada] in abc.es {{in lang|es}}</ref> Investigation still does not rule out an involvement of the husband.<ref>[http://www.abc.es/espana/castilla-la-mancha/toledo/pueblos/abci-crimen-quintanar-misterio-cuchillos-201801102041_noticia.html Crimen de Quintanar: el misterio de los dos cuchillos] in abc.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 22: A man (41) shoots his ex-partner (37) in [[Zaragoza]].<ref>[https://www.heraldo.es/noticias/aragon/zaragoza-provincia/zaragoza/2016/02/22/nuevo-caso-violencia-genero-zaragoza-deja-dos-muertos-bar-miralbueno-777564-301.html Un hombre asesina a tiros a su expareja y luego se suicida en un bar de Miralbueno] in heraldo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*March 14: A man (46) is accused of stabbing his partner (34) in [[Gij\u00f3n]], [[Province of Asturias|Asturias]].<ref>[http://www.lne.es/gijon/2016/03/14/asesinan-mujer-34-anos-gijon/1896919.html La pareja de la mujer asesinada en Gij\u00f3n cree que pudo apu\u00f1alarla durante una discusi\u00f3n] in La Nueva Espa\u00f1a {{in lang|es}}.</ref> Finally he was sentenced to 4 years for reckless homicide as the judge considered that he had stabbed her in a struggle to try to pick the knife from her hands, but without intending to kill her.<ref>[https://www.heraldo.es/noticias/nacional/2018/06/07/cuatro-anos-carcel-por-imprudencia-grave-matar-mujer-con-cuchillo-1248165-305.html Cuatro a\u00f1os de c\u00e1rcel por imprudencia grave y matar a su mujer con un cuchillo] in heraldo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*April 12: A man (49) stabs his partner (48) in [[Benidorm]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://cadenaser.com/emisora/2016/04/12/radio_alicante/1460474731_480892.html Una mujer asesinada en Benidorm a manos de su pareja] in cadenaser.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*April 14: A [[Mossos d'Esquadra|mosso d'Esquadra]] (45) shoots his ex-partner (36) in front of their 7-year-old daughter. Then he commits suicide. In [[Sant Feliu de Llobregat]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/sociedad/dEsquadra-asesina-presuntamente-pareja-Barcelona_0_505349602.html Un mosso d'Esquadra asesina a su expareja en Barcelona en un presunto caso de violencia machista] in eldiario.es {{in lang|es}}</ref> \n*July 24: A man is arrested accused of suffocating his wife (49) in [[Bilbao]].<ref>[http://www.eitb.eus/es/noticias/sociedad/detalle/4276228/violencia-machista-bilbao-mujer-asesinada-pasado-sabado/ Una mujer fue asesinada por su pareja el pasado s\u00e1bado en Bilbao] in eib.eus {{in lang|es}}</ref> He was acquitted for lack of evidence in 2018.<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/pais-vasco/2018/05/22/5b04553c268e3e42778b462c.html Absuelto por falta de pruebas el acusado de asfixiar a su pareja en Bilbao] en elmundo.es</ref>\n\n===Other cases===\n* July 7: [[La Manada sexual abuse case]]: A group of five men sexually abused an 18-year-old girl in a portal.<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thelocal.es/20171124/anger-in-spain-over-pamplona-festival-gang-rape-case |title=Anger in Spain over Pamplona festival gang rape case |date=November 24, 2017 |publisher=The Local |accessdate=April 29, 2018}}</ref>\n*August 21\u201322: [[Murder of Diana Quer]]: An 18-year-old woman is abducted and murdered.<ref>https://www.elespanol.com/espana/20180101/prision-incomunicada-sin-chicle-asesino-diana-quer/273972844_0.html</ref>\n*August 24, 2016: A man ties his ex-wife to her bed and beats her in front of their children in [[Villa de Vallecas]].<ref>.[http://www.europapress.es/madrid/noticia-condenado-nueve-anos-carcel-hombre-drogo-expareja-ato-cama-golpeo-toda-noche-20180226152554.html Condenado a nueve a\u00f1os de c\u00e1rcel un hombre que drog\u00f3 a su expareja, la at\u00f3 a la cama y la golpe\u00f3 durante toda la noche] in [[Europapress]]</ref>\n\n== 2017 ==\n===Gender violence murders===\n50 women were killed in gender violence cases.<ref>[http://www.violenciagenero.igualdad.mpr.gob.es/violenciaEnCifras/victimasMortales/fichaMujeres/pdf/Vmortales_31_12_2017(1).pdf Official data] in Health Ministry web</ref>\n*January 4: A man (20) stabs and kills his partner (40) in [[Rivas-Vaciamadrid]]<ref>[http://www.abc.es/espana/madrid/abci-este-nelson-presunto-asesino-profesora-universitaria-rivas-201701040127_noticia.html Este es Nelson: el presunto asesino de la profesora universitaria de Rivas] in abc.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 15: A man (31) slays his ex-partner (33) in [[Hu\u00e9rcal de Almer\u00eda|Hu\u00e9rcal]], [[Province of Almer\u00eda|Almer\u00eda]]<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/andalucia/2017/01/15/587b60a122601db2018b456f.html Muere una mujer en Almer\u00eda degollada por su ex, con el que hab\u00eda mantenido una breve relaci\u00f3n] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 17: A man confesses to have cut his wife's (48) throat and thrown the corpse to a river in [[Burlada]], [[Navarre]].<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/sociedad/2017/01/16/587cff1b46163f762b8b457a.html Contin\u00faa la b\u00fasqueda del cuerpo de la mujer asesinada en Navarra] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 28: A man (59) stabs his wife (55) in [[O Carballino]], [[Province of Orense|Orense]].<ref>[https://www.lavozdegalicia.es/noticia/ourense/o-carballino/2017/01/29/hombre-mata-mujer-cuchilladas-intenta-suicidarse-carballino/00031485722086750588223.htm Un hombre asesina a su mujer en O Carballi\u00f1o] in [[La Voz de Galicia]]. {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 30: Woman (40) killed by her husband (40) in [[Sese\u00f1a]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]]<ref>[http://www.abc.es/espana/castilla-la-mancha/toledo/pueblos/abci-hallan-muerta-casa-quinon-mujer-201701281428_noticia.html Detienen a la pareja de la mujer hallada muerta en Sese\u00f1a con signos de violencia] in abc.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 5: A man (44) stabs his wife (38) in [[Mora, Spain|Mora]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]].<ref>[http://www.abc.es/espana/castilla-la-mancha/toledo/pueblos/abci-mujer-asesinada-mora-pidio-auxilio-mensaje-telefonico-201702062203_noticia.html La mujer asesinada en Mora pidi\u00f3 auxilio en un mensaje telef\u00f3nico] in abc.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 7: A man (82) kills his wife (79) while she was sleeping in [[S\u00faria]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20170207/mujer-muere-apunalada-marido-suria-crimen-machista-5791211 Carmen, la primera v\u00edctima del machismo del a\u00f1o en Catalunya] in elperiodico.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 11: A [[Civil Guard (Spain)|civil guard]] (31) shoots his partner (26) and later commits suicide in [[Sese\u00f1a]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]].<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/sociedad/2017/02/12/58a032aa46163f1c3a8b465e.html La mujer hallada muerta en Sese\u00f1a fue asesinada por su pareja, un guardia civil, que se suicid\u00f3] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 13: A man (57) stabs to death his wife (46) and her daughter (18), his stepdaughter, in [[Daimiel]], [[Province of Ciudad Real|Ciudad Real]].<ref>[http://www.hoy.es/sociedad/201702/13/hombre-mata-mujer-hija-20170213103410-rc.html Detenido por matar a pu\u00f1aladas a su esposa e hijastra en Daimiel] in hoy.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 19: A man (86) stabs his wife (79) in a nursing home care in [[El Campello|Campello]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://elpais.com/ccaa/2017/02/19/valencia/1487506564_859847.html Una mujer, asesinada a cuchilladas por su marido en una residencia de ancianos] en elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 20: A man (47) explodes two [[butane cylinder]]s to kill his ex-partner (52) in [[Redondela]], [[Province of Pontevedra|Pontevedra]]. Both die.<ref>[https://www.lavozdegalicia.es/noticia/vigo/redondela/2017/02/21/explosion-mata-chapela-pareja-tramitaba-separacion/0003_201702C21P2991.htm Vuela la casa y mata a su expareja en Redondela] in lavozdegalicia.es {{in lang|es}}\n</ref>\n*February 21: A man stabs his ex-partner (34) in [[Santa Perpetua de Moguda|Santa Perpetua]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.lainformacion.com/policia-y-justicia/policia/Detenido-Santa-Perpetua-muerte-expareja_0_1001900008.html Detenido un vecino de Santa Perpetua por asesinar a su expareja de 34 a\u00f1os] in lainformacion.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 21: A man (54) is arrested accused of throwing out his ex-partner (48) out of the hollow of a staircase of a building in [[Valencia]].<ref>[http://www.levante-emv.com/sucesos/2017/02/24/mandar-colombianos-matar-puta/1533056.html \"Te voy a mandar a unos colombianos y te voy a matar, puta\"] in [[Levante-EMV]] {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 21: A woman (47) appears dead in [[Gand\u00eda]], [[Province of Valencia|Valencia]]. A man with [[restraining order]] is arrested.<ref>[http://www.levante-emv.com/sucesos/2017/02/23/guardia-civil-retirada-muerta-gandia/1532631.html La guardia civil retirada muerta en Gandia recibi\u00f3 un fuerte golpe en la cabeza] in Levante-EMV {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 22: In [[Villanueva del Fresno]], [[Province of Badajoz|Badajoz]] a woman (91) dies due to the stabbing wounds inflicted by her husband (91) two days prior.<ref>[http://www.elperiodicoextremadura.com/noticias/extremadura/fallece-mujer-villanueva-fresno-herida-marido-cuello_1000301.html Fallece la mujer de Villanueva del Fresno herida por su marido en el cuello] in elperiodico.com {{in lang|es}}</ref> The sons does not consider this a gender violence case,<ref>[http://www.europapress.es/sociedad/sucesos-00649/noticia-hijos-anciana-villanueva-fresno-afirman-no-sido-violencia-genero-acto-compasion-20170225134712.html Los hijos de la anciana de Villanueva del Fresno afirman que no ha sido violencia de g\u00e9nero sino un \"acto de compasi\u00f3n] in europapress.com {{in lang|es}}</ref> but is counted as such by the Ministry.<ref>[http://www.publico.es/sociedad/violencia-machista-asesinadas-violencia-machista.html Los primeros 53 d\u00edas de 2017, el peor periodo de violencia machista en 10 a\u00f1os] in publico.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*March 1: A man slaughters his partner (32) and then manipulates the gas pipes to cause an explosion and commit suicide. In Madrid.<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/madrid/2017/03/01/58b6a03ee2704ebd0f8b458a.html  Un hombre asesina a su pareja y trata de suicidarse provocando una explosi\u00f3n en su vivienda de Vic\u00e1lvaro] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*March 29: A man (47) strangles his wife (42) and smothers their two children (ages, 5 and 8). Then he commits suicide by throwing himself out the window. in [[Campo de Criptana]], [[Province of Ciudad Real|Ciudad Real]].<ref>[https://politica.elpais.com/politica/2017/03/29/actualidad/1490779946_350665.html Asesinados una mujer y sus dos hijos en un piso de Campo de Criptana] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*March 31: A man (34) strangles his partner (23) and then surrenders to the police in [[Telde]], [[Gran Canaria]].<ref>[https://www.teldeactualidad.com/hemeroteca/noticia/sucesos/2017/03/31/3658.html Un joven de Telde estrangula a su novia en Lomo Magullo y se entrega a la Polic\u00eda] in teldeactualidad.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*April 4: A man (36) beats to death his partner (44) and then tries to burn the house in [[San Crist\u00f3bal de La Laguna|La Laguna]], [[Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife|Santa Cruz de Tenerife]].<ref>[http://eldia.es/sucesos/2017-04-05/4-pareja-asesinada-confeso-crimen-sanitarios.htm La pareja de la asesinada confes\u00f3 el crimen a sanitarios] in eldia.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*April 10: A man (24) beats to death his partner (29) in [[El Alqui\u00e1n]], [[Almer\u00eda]] and then commits suicide by hanging.<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/andalucia/2017/04/10/58eba86322601d90758b45f0.html Mata a su ex pareja de un golpe en la cabeza y luego se ahorca en Almer\u00eda] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*April 21: A man (38) strangles his partner (45) in [[Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20170424/dictada-prision-provisional-para-acusado-matar-pareja-raval-5993595 Los Mossos confirman que el homicidio del Raval es un crimen machista] in elperiodico.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 2: A man stabs and kills his partner (44) and their child in [[Alcobendas]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]].<ref>[https://elpais.com/ccaa/2017/05/02/madrid/1493721962_851880.html?id_externo_rsoc=whatsapp Una mujer de 44 a\u00f1os y su hijo de 12, muertos a cuchilladas en Madrid] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 5: A man strangles his wife (39), puts the corpse in a suitcase and throws it to a river in [[Alcolea del R\u00edo]], [[Province of Sevilla|Sevilla]].<ref>[http://www.diariodesevilla.es/provincia/cinismo-asesino_0_1134187173.html El cinismo del asesino] in diariodesvilla.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 12: A man (40) kills ex-partner (27) and confesses to the police in Madrid.<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/madrid/2017/05/30/592c7107ca4741275b8b457f.html La abuela que reclama a sus nietos, hu\u00e9rfanos por la violencia machista] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 21: A man sets fire to the car in which he and his partner (48) were, both burned to death in [[La Llagosta]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://elpais.com/ccaa/2017/08/05/catalunya/1501949426_236845.html La mujer muerta en La Llagosta fue calcinada por su pareja] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 26: A woman (55) is strangled by her husband (61) who tries to commit suicide by stabbing himself. In Madrid.<ref>[https://www.elespanol.com/reportajes/20170528/219478243_0.html Susana, la terapeuta de Reiki que fue estrangulada por su marido reci\u00e9n jubilado] in elespanol.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 27: A man (48) stabs his co-worker and ex-partner (31) in [[Molina de Segura]], [[Province of Murcia|Murcia]].<ref>[http://www.laopiniondemurcia.es/comunidad/2017/05/30/nieto-ayudar-llevar-dolor-derruido/833369.html Mi nieto me va a ayudar a llevar el dolor, estoy derruido] in laopiniondemurcia {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 27: A man (43) strangles with a plastic bag his partner (37) in [[Collado Villalba]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]].<ref>[http://aquienlasierra.es/2017/05/27/una-mujer-37-aparece-muerta-collado-villalba-amordazada-una-bolsa-plastico-cubriendole-la-cabeza/ Una mujer de 37 a\u00f1os aparece muerta en Collado Villalba, amordazada y con una bolsa de pl\u00e1stico en la cabeza ] in aquienlasierra {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*June 13: A man (51) shots his partner (55) in [[Las Gabias]], [[Province of Granada|Granada]].<ref>[http://cadenaser.com/emisora/2017/06/13/radio_granada/1497332940_350986.html Encarnaci\u00f3n, asesinada por su pareja en Las Gabias] in cadenaser.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*June 24: A man stabs his ex-partner (39) in front of her 6-year-old child in [[Seville]].<ref>[http://diario16.com/nuevo-crimen-machista-sevilla/ Nuevo crimen machista en Sevilla] in diario16.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*June 25: A man (43) stabs his partner (29) in a car and surrenders to the police in [[Salou]], [[Province of Tarragona|Tarragona]].<ref>[https://www.diariodepontevedra.es/articulo/espana/un-hombre-se-entrega-los-mossos-tras-matar-su-pareja-en-salou/20170625151103331070.html Un hombre se entrega a los Mossos tras matar a su pareja en Salou] in diariodepontevedra.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*July 15: A man (71) kills with an axe his wife (66) in [[Hu\u00e9scar]], [[Province of Granada|Granada]].<ref>[https://www.infolibre.es/noticias/politica/2017/07/15/un_mujer_asesinada_por_marido_huescar_granada_67627_1012.html Un mujer es asesinada por su marido en Hu\u00e9scar (Granada)] in infolibre.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*July 17: A man beats to death his partner (38) and then burnts the house in [[Valencia]].<ref>[http://www.levante-emv.com/comunitat-valenciana/2017/07/23/prision-pareja-mujer-asesinada-valencia/1596821.html Prisi\u00f3n para la pareja de la mujer asesinada en Val\u00e8ncia] in levante-emv.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*August 2: A man (71) beats to death his wife (63) and surrenders to the police in [[Getafe]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]].<ref>[https://www.infolibre.es/noticias/politica/2017/08/02/un_hombre_entrega_policia_getafe_tras_confesar_que_mato_golpes_mujer_68283_1012.html Un hombre se entrega a la Polic\u00eda en Getafe tras confesar que mat\u00f3 a golpes a su mujer] in infolibre.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*August 5: A man (39) beats to death his partner (38) in [[Santa Cruz de Tenerife]].<ref>[https://www.huffingtonpost.es/2017/08/07/la-mujer-asesinada-en-tenerife-es-una-nueva-victima-de-violencia_a_23068084/ Ana Bel\u00e9n G. P, la mujer asesinada e