 4: A man (24) [[Defenestration|defenestrates]] his partner (26) in [[Madrid]]<ref>.[https://www.elconfidencial.com/espana/2017-01-04/mujer-asesinada-violencia-genero-pareja_1312222/ La mujer que cay\u00f3 por la ventana el d\u00eda de A\u00f1o Nuevo es un caso de violencia de g\u00e9nero] in elconfidencial.com {{in lang|es}}</ref> The man was charged for mistreatment, but not murder.\n*January 18: A man (78) suffocates his wife (79) with a pillow, then commits suicide. He left a [[suicide note|note]] explaining that he did that to end her suffering as she had [[Alzheimer's disease|Alzheimer]].<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/madrid/2017/01/18/587f4d3c22601d276a8b4585.html Un hombre mata a su mujer, que padec\u00eda alzheimer, y luego se quita la vida] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 3: A father, (27) after an argument with his wife in a hospital in Madrid, picks up their 1-year-old child and throws himself out of a window, killing both.<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/madrid/2017/02/03/5894454a268e3ee7348b4730.html Un padre mata a su hija al tirarse al vac\u00edo con ella tras discutir con su mujer en el Hospital de La Paz] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 18: A woman (55) denounces the partner (29) of her niece whom he had tried to strangle. He kills the complainant before the police can arrest him. In [[Caudete]], [[Province of Albacete|Albacete]].<ref>[http://cadenaser.com/emisora/2017/05/19/radio_albacete/1495194010_056585.html La mujer asesinada en Caudete denunci\u00f3 hace un a\u00f1o a su agresor por amenazas] in cadenaser.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*May 24: A man (48) who had been accused of gender abuse by his wife (45) 7 years prior has a [[sex change]] during the judicial process and claims that [[Ley Org\u00e1nica de Medidas de Protecci\u00f3n Integral contra la Violencia de G\u00e9nero|Spanish gender violence law]] no longer applies to the case.<ref>[https://elpais.com/elpais/2017/05/26/inenglish/1495788642_609014.html Spanish fireman accus