er in 2003 and the new victim was his lawyer.<ref>[https://elpais.com/sociedad/2019/01/18/actualidad/1547799798_528873.html Un hombre que asesin\u00f3 a su esposa en 2003 mata a su abogada, con la que manten\u00eda una relaci\u00f3n] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 26: A man (68) kills his wife (69) with an axe in [[Dos Hermanas]], [[Province of Sevilla|Sevilla]].<ref>[https://sevilla.abc.es/provincia/dos-hermanas/sevi-mujer-acaba-asesinada-pareja-hermanas-hacha-201901261858_noticia.html Detenido un var\u00f3n por asesinar con un hacha a su mujer en el domicilio familiar de Dos Hermanas] in abc.es</ref>\n*January 30: A man (19) hits and beheads his partner (17) in [[Reus]], [[Province of Tarragona|Tarragona]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20190131/46110818026/asesinato-violencia-machista-reus.html Brutal asesinato en Reus de una joven de 17 a\u00f1os por su pareja] in lavanguardia.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 3: A man (57) beats to death his partner (60), who was also his [[aunt]], in [[Santa Cruz de Tenerife]].<ref>[https://elpais.com/sociedad/2019/02/04/actualidad/1549274450_997983.html Detenido un hombre acusado de matar a golpes a su pareja en Tenerife] in elpais.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 8: In the freezer of a man (42) is found the quartered corpse of his girlfriend (22) who disappeared in 2017. In [[Alcal\u00e1 de Henares]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]].<ref>[https://www.larazon.es/local/madrid/la-autopsia-confirma-que-la-joven-descuartizada-en-alcala-es-la-pareja-del-detenido-AC21896655 La autopsia confirma que la joven descuartizada en Alcal\u00e1 es la pareja del detenido] in larazon.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*February 9: A man (34) hits and slaughters his partner (29) and tries to pass it for a suicide. In [[Planes, Alicante|Planes]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.diarioinformacion.com/sucesos/2019/02/15/guardia-civil-sostiene-apresado-asesinato/2118369.htmlLa Guardia Civil sostiene que el ap