o-hombre-matar-mujer-castellbisbal-7710016 Detenido un hombre tras matar a su mujer en Castellbisbal] in elperiodico.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*November 25: A man (29) cuts the throat of his partner (26) in [[Por\u00eds de Abona|Abona]], [[Province of Tenerife|Tenerife]].<ref>[https://www.telecinco.es/informativos/sociedad/sara-victima-violencia-genero-degollada_18_2857845023.html Sara, asesinada por su novio en Tenerife fue degollada y apu\u00f1alada en el cuello varias veces] in telecinco.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*November 29: A man (93) kills with [[cold weapon]] his wife in (86) en [[Izn\u00e1jar]], [[Province of C\u00f3rdoba (Spain)|C\u00f3rdoba]].<ref>[https://www.diariocordoba.com/noticias/cordobaprovincia/detenido-marido-mujer-86-anos-hallada-muerta-arma-blanca-iznajar_1339546.html Detenido el marido de la mujer de 86 a\u00f1os hallada muerta por arma blanca en Izn\u00e1jar] in diariocordoba.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*December 2: A man (44) cuts the throat of his partner (36) in [[El Prat de Llobregat]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.telecinco.es/informativos/sociedad/yulia-asesinada-violencia-machista_18_2860995016.html Yulia, degollada por su marido, no hab\u00eda denunciado] in telecinco.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n\n===Other cases===\n*January 1: 4 men (19, 21, 22 and 24 years old) [[Gang rape|rape]] a woman (19) in [[Callosa d'en Sarri\u00e0]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.elconfidencial.com/espana/comunidad-valenciana/2019-01-08/callosa-pamplona-manada-violacion_1745614/ La jueza instruye el caso de La Manada de Callosa como violaci\u00f3n y con penas m\u00e1ximas] in elconfidencial.com {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*January 8: A sentence of [[Supreme Court of Spain]] concludes that a man hitting his (female) partner is always gender violence, even if both have mutually hit each other.<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2019/01/08/5c34c8d9fc6c83eb128b467b.html El Supremo: \"Toda agresi\u00f3n de un hombre a una mujer en relaci\u00f3n de pareja o ex pareja es violencia de g\u00e9nero\"] in elmundo.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n* February 3: Six men are detained for allegedly gang raping an 18-year-old woman in [[Sabadell]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.cope.es/actualidad/espana/noticias/manada-sabadell-los-mossos-interrogaran-hoy-los-detenidos-20190204_345578 La 'manada' de Sabadell: Los mossos interrogar\u00e1n hoy a los 6 detenidos] in cope.es {{in lang|es}}</ref>\n*Npvember 30: A man was arrested for the alleged murder of his wife (38) in [[Vic\u00e1lvaro]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]], but was acquitted in March 2020 when the autopsy confirmed that the cause of death was a heart attack.<ref>[https://www.elespanol.com/sociedad/20200304/alexia-infarto-justicia-absuelve-detenido-presunto-homicidio/472203254_0.html Alexia muri\u00f3 de un infarto: absuelto el detenido por un presunto homicidio machista ] in elespanol.com {{in lang|es}</ref>\n\n== 2020 ==\n===Gender violence murders===\n*January 6: A man (27) is arrested accused of killing his partner (28) and their 3 year old daughter in [[Esplugues de Llobregat]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[http://www.rtve.es/noticias/20200106/detenido-hombre-matar-su-mujer-su-hija-su-casa-esplugues-llobregat-barcelona/1994951.shtml Detenido un hombre por matar a su mujer y a su hija en su casa de Esplugues de Llobregat, Barcelona] in rtve.es</ref>\n*January 12: A man (53) shots his partner (61) then commits suicide. In [[Puertollano]], [[Province of Ciudad Real|Ciudad Real]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/sucesos/20200113/472860131699/muertos-hombre-mujer-violencia-puertollano-ciudad-real.html Un hombre mata a su pareja y se suicida en Puertollano] in lavanguardia.com</ref>\n*January, 18: A [[Mossos d'Esquadra|''Mosso d'Esquadra'']] (42) shots his partner (29) in [[Terrassa]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]].<ref>[https://www.lavanguardia.com/vida/20200119/472964333206/mosso-terrassa-violencia-machista.html Un Mosso mata a tiros a su expareja y se suicida in Terrassa] in lavanguardia.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 22: A man (50) kills his wife (43) in front of their 11 and 14 years old sons. In [[La Puebla de Almoradiel]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]].<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/espana/2020/01/22/5e27fb1421efa008218b468d.html Mata a su esposa en La Puebla de Almoradiel en presencia de sus dos hijos] in elmundo.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 22: A man (77) stabs his wife (73) in [[Caniles]], [[Province of Granada|Granada]].<ref>[https://www.20minutos.es/noticia/4126864/0/detenido-por-matar-a-punaladas-a-su-mujer-en-caniles-granada/ Un hombre de 77 a\u00f1os mata a pu\u00f1aladas a su mujer, de 73, en Caniles (Granada)] in 20minutos.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 25: A man (81) stabs his wife (79), then commits suicide. In [[A Pastoriza]], [[Province of Lugo|Lugo]]. The family indicates that the agressor had senile [[dementia]].<ref>[https://www.lavozdegalicia.es/noticia/lugo/a-pastoriza/2020/01/26/mujer-asesinada-pastoriza-murio-punalada-costado/00031580068839323575648.htm La mujer asesinada en A Pastoriza muri\u00f3 de una pu\u00f1alada en un costado] in lavozdegalicia.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*January, 28: A man (45) suffocates his partner (40) in [[Sant Joan Desp\u00ed]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]] and is arrested at the airport while he was trying to escape.<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200127/un-hombre-asesina-a-su-pareja-en-sant-joan-despi-7824877 https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200127/un-hombre-asesina-a-su-pareja-en-sant-joan-despi-7824877] in elperiodico.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 3: An ex-[[Spanish Legion|legionary]] alleguedly kills in [[Gij\u00f3n]], [[Asturias]], his expartner, then scapes.<ref>[https://www.elcomercio.es/asturias/encuentran-muerta-mujer-calzada-gijon-presunto-caso-violencia-genero-20200203151255-nt.html Encuentran muerta a una mujer en Gij\u00f3n en un caso de violencia de g\u00e9nero] in elcomercio.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 7: A man (47) beheads his partner (49) in [[Lugo]].<ref>[https://www.republica.com/2020/02/09/el-novio-de-la-mujer-asesinada-en-lugo-pasara-a-disposicion-judicial/# El novio de la mujer asesinada en Lugo pasar\u00e1 a disposici\u00f3n judicial] in republica.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 8: A legionary (24) stabs his expartner (38) in [[Granada]].<ref>[https://www.ideal.es/granada/mujer-fallecida-apunalada-por-su-expareja-tras-20200208192928-nt.html Un legionario destinado en Viator mata a pu\u00f1aladas a su expareja en Granada] in ideal.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 17: A man (59) stabs his partner (34) in [[Moraira]], [[Province of Alicante|Alicante]].<ref>[https://www.diarioinformacion.com/sucesos/2020/02/19/pareja-mujer-asesinada-moraira-confiesa/2236393.html El marido de la mujer asesinada en Moraira se entrega y confiesa el crimen] in diarioinformacion.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 26: A man (51) shoots his wife (43) in front of their 4 years old son, then commits suicide. In [[Aznalc\u00f3llar]], [[Province of Sevilla|Sevilla]].<ref>[https://www.edmradio.es/2020/02/26/una-mujer-es-asesinada-por-su-pareja-en-aznalcollar/ UNA MUJER ES ASESINADA POR SU PAREJA EN AZNALC\u00d3LLAR] in edmradio.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*February 26: A man (76) stabs his wife (75) in [[Fuenlabrada]], [[Province of Madrid|Madrid]].<ref>[https://alcabodelacalle.es/un-hombre-asesina-a-su-mujer-en-su-casa-de-fuenlabrada-y-despues-intenta-suicidarse Un hombre asesina a su mujer en su casa de Fuenlabrada y despu\u00e9s intenta suicidarse] in alcabodelacalle.es] (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 2: A man (69) stabs his ex-wife (65) in [[Posadas, Spain|Posadas]], [[Province of C\u00f3rdoba|C\u00f3rdoba]] then tries to commit suicide.<ref>[https://www.elmundo.es/andalucia/2020/03/02/5e5d0627fc6c835f3a8b461f.html Un hombre de 69 a\u00f1os asesina a su mujer en Posadas (C\u00f3rdoba)] in elmundo.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 9: A man shots his girldfriend (37) in [[Villanueva de Castell\u00f3n]], [[Province of Valencia|Valencia]].<ref>[https://www.lasprovincias.es/sucesos/joven-muere-recibir-20200309001635-ntvo.html?ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.es%2F Un hombre con antecedentes policiales mata a su pareja de un tiro en la cabeza en Villanueva de Castell\u00f3n] in lasprovincias.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 11: A man (60) stabs his wife (56) and their daughter (24) in [[Abanto y Ci\u00e9rvana-Abanto Zierbena|Abanto Zierbena]], [[Biscay]].<ref>[https://www.levante-emv.com/espana/2020/03/11/madre-hija-halladas-muertas-vizcaya/1988275.html Detenido tras matar a su mujer y su hija en Vizcaya] in levante-emv.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*March 19: A man (35) kills his wife (35) in front of their children in [[Almassora]], [[Province of Castell\u00f3n|Castell\u00f3n]].<ref>[https://www.elperiodico.com/es/sociedad/20200320/un-hombre-mata-a-su-mujer-delante-de-sus-hijos-en-castellon-7897934 Un hombre mata a su mujer delante de sus hijos en Castell\u00f3n] in elperiodico.com (in Spanish)</ref>\n*April 4: A man (62) strangles his wife (78) in [[Las Palmas de Gran Canaria]].<ref>[https://www.eldiario.es/canariasahora/sociedad/delegacion-asesinato-machista-Palmas-Gran-Canaria_0_1013148842.html Asesinada por su marido una mujer de 78 a\u00f1os en Las Palmas de Gran Canaria] in eldiario.es (in Spanish)</ref>\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Human_rights_in_Spain#Migrant agricultural workers in Southern Spain|Violence against migrant agricultural workers in Spain]]\n* [[List of incidents of violence against women]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [http://www.violenciagenero.igualdad.mpr.gob.es/otrasFormas/home.htm Violence against women] in Ministry of Health website {{in lang|es}}\n* [http://ibasque.com/mujeres-muertas-en-espana-por-violencia-machista/ MUJERES ASESINADAS EN ESPA\u00d1A POR VIOLENCIA DE G\u00c9NERO y MACHISTA en 2019] in ibasque.com {{in lang|es}}\n\n[[Category:Incidents of violence against women|*]]\n[[Category:Violence against women in Spain|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of events in Spain|Incidents of violence against women]]\n", "name_user": "Federico1984", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eOther cases", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_incidents_of_violence_against_women_in_Spain"}
